Expense tracker

Web frontend.

javascript
- Should be built with React for the UI components
- Use Tailwind CSS for styling to keep the design consistent
- Chart.js or Recharts for visualizing spending trends
- React Router for navigation between different views
- Axios for API calls to the backend
- web page should be viewable on all devices.

Options
- list daily spend
- Weekly spend
- monthly spend
- yearly spend
- custom date range

Backend

- Postgres database
- REST API with Express.js for CRUD operations
- Authentication using JWT tokens
- Background job for generating monthly summary reports
- Redis cache for frequently accessed spending totals
